metadata.description:
No Face by Jack Frost (Episode 1)

Jack Frost is an Alien DJ, Metaverse Defender, and Intergalactic Hero. In this Pilot Episode, our hero introduces himself to the Universe and lays down a few basic ground rules and expectations. 

"I'm from outer space. You can't see my face.
There's a lazer on my waist and I'm gone without a trace."

The song is called No Face. It is intentionally simple and repetitive and it is meant to become a war chant for the Aliens as we make our way through web3.

Shout out to my homie Gart on the cover art. He's a beast and we will get him into web3 soon.

Mint this free Music NFT and collect it forever. Or get two or three and trade the others on a secondary market like OpenSea for a profit. Or you can mint 10 of them, I don't care and we won't judge you. 

Web3 is meant to be fun. Enjoy your life and celebrate music and art and technology and humanity and Aliens and family and love. And remember, everything you want is on the other side of fear. 

Peace,
Jack Frost
